chat.msg: hey, estas listo?
I am ready
nice! okay, i'm at the starting point
i see a twig to my left leading towards an island with a tiger. what should i do next?
follow towards the tiger
alright, i'm at the tiger island
now where to?
go left. You should see a twig leading towards an island with a parrot and an elephant
found the parrot island! and there's an elephant here too
where should i go from here?
go down and right until you get to some rocks that lead to an island with a tree frog
got it, i'm now on the island with the frog
now go left across the crocodile and back onto the island with the parrot and elephant
easy peasy
back to the elephant island i go! now where?
go left across the rocks to an island with a giraffe on it
alright, i see the giraffe! now to where?
go down to the next island that should have a snake on it.
yikes! snake spotted! what's next?
go past it, and you should be at the treasure.
awesome! got to the treasure! *finished*

chat.msg: hey, q tal? empezamos el juego?
yeah, ready to play :-D
great! look at the map
notice the white dog on your right? i want you to stroll a few steps to your left, dodging a wooden bench, until you touch a trail leading to a florist stand. got it?
got it! what's next?
nice job! now, make a sharp 180-degree turn to your left and cross back over that trail
keep going until you're back by our white dog. cool, huh?
I'm back at the white dog
rad! now you're going to cross the branch to your south
just keep going straight down
I'm across the branch
you're doing great! now just stroll over the picnic mat and try not to eat those delicious looking berries in the bowl
I'm there. These berries look delicious ha
tempting, right? now let's move on
cross over the wooden branch to the north. you're almost at another spot
I'm across the branch
great! now, you see that green bush? let's circle it from the right
make sure not to touch it. we want to keep it nice and green
got it
nice! we're heading to the florist's stand now
check it out yet?
Checking it out now
lovely! tuck in left, sneak under that stand, and head toward that big bridge
see those bikers? let's pass them
just passed the bikers
cool! keep going until you see two old folks just past the bridge, sitting on a bench and reading newspapers
see them?
yes
awesome! now walk just a few steps south
notice another wooden branch and a pretty green bush? that's your next marker!
at the branch now!
you're nailing this! guide your steps east, sneak between the branch and the bush
done!
absolute legend! just walk a few more steps to the east, and
wait, what's that brown creature over there? you are there, well done!
what next
nothing more, my friend
you've reached the final objective. awesome job! let's play again soon, alright?

chat.msg: hi there! que comience el juego!!
Hi, lets play!
awesome! i see a tent at the north
where to from here buddy?
so for your first step you will head south just past the dog and then turn left
alrighty! passed the dog and turned left
what's the next step, amigo?
go up and over the camp fire and around it until you get past the mushrooms
okay, i went past the fire and the mushrooms
what's next?
once you're there go south and back onto the dirt trail.
back on the dirt trail heading south, done! now where?
follow the dirt trail until you're just south of the telesope
okay, i'm south of the telescope now
what's next in our adventure?
after that cut through the grass to the right of the telescope and back onto the trail
alright, cut through the grass, back on the trail
head left down the trail and then back up onto the grass
left down the trail, back onto the grass
done! what's next, my good friend?
go up to the log cabin, and then you're there!
made it to the log cabin! we did it, buddy! *finished*

chat.msg: hola, q tal? ready to play?
hi, ready to play :-D
great! okay, you see those three palm trees nearby? first, go under the first tree heading south-west. then, make a quick right past the second palm and sharply left before the third one
continue south from there. got it?
yeah
cool! now, you see that adorable brown puppy there? go left around it, then sort of sway to the left and then over again to the right, heading due south
got it
sweet, now up ahead you'll see a big rock on the left and a smaller one to the right
just walk right through them till you hit the water. done?
done!
awesome! now, in the water you'll see a big red crab, take a right around him and keep the big rock on your side, continue heading west
done! what's next?
see that medium-sized rock up ahead? head towards it, but watch out for the shark in the water! when you get close, make a sharp turn to the right
done!
great job avoiding that shark! now, let's get back to dry land
walk between the medium rock and a colorful ball, and keep going north. done?
I'm right by the colorful ball
perfect! now, head slightly left towards the northwest
you'll see a red tent to your left and a big speaker to your right. get in between them
done
nice one! now, go around the tent like you're drawing a big half-circle
done
sweet! now, head south towards the water, but stop just short of getting your feet wet again
got it?
got it!
good, take a quick right and duck under that red kayak next to you
keep going west
I'm there!
cool beans! now, turn north, stroll along the kayak, and stop when you reach a little green bush
should be just a few steps away
